PR 201403-PSA (NSCB-CAR)-01
PRESS RELEASE
27 MARCH 2014
2014 Agency Release Calendar for CAR is now online
The consolidated 2014 Agency Release Calendar (ARC) for the Cordillera Administrative Region
(CAR) can now be accessed online. The ARC is the schedule of statistical outputs of selected
government agencies. For every source agency, the ARC contains information on what statistical data
are available, period covered, level of disaggregation, schedule of data release, form of output (e.g.,
print, e-copy and/or web download), as well as the contact person and telephone number(s).
The 2014 ARC of the region can be accessed at the ARC section on the Philippine Statistics Authority
(NSCB-CAR) website http://www.nscb.gov.ph/rucar/arc.htm. For easy reference and navigation,
drop-down menus are provided for each agency release calendar and for each month of the year.
The complete 2014 ARC document can be downloaded in two (2) PDF files: release calendar sorted
by agency (http://www.nscb.gov.ph/rucar/pdf/arc/2014%20ARC%20by%20agency.pdf) and release
calendar sorted by month of release (http://www.nscb.gov.ph/rucar/pdf/arc/2014%20ARC%20
by%20month.pdf ).
The ARC is prepared annually by the PSA-NSCB to promote transparency, timeliness, and
accessibility of government statistics.
